---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Date Night Candle Making"
  description="Create custom candles together for a romantic date night in Centerville, TN."
  price="$30-40 per couple"
  duration="2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="date night candles, couple activity, romantic date, candle making"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Date Night Candle Making - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Make memories and beautiful candles together. This romantic candle-making experience is perfect for couples looking for a unique, creative date night.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Pour custom-scented candles while enjoying quality time together. You'll each create your own candle or collaborate on a shared design. Our romantic setting makes this the perfect date experience.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Premium soy wax and supplies</li>
      <li>40+ fragrance options to choose from</li>
      <li>Beautiful container selection</li>
      <li>Expert pouring guidance</li>
      <li>Romantic atmosphere</li>
      <li>Take-home finished candles immediately</li>
      <li>Café refreshments available</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Date nights seeking something special</li>
      <li>Anniversary celebrations</li>
      <li>Romantic bonding time</li>
      <li>Creating matching candles together</li>
      <li>Couples wanting quality time</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and fragrance selection (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Choose containers and colors (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Hands-on candle pouring together (60 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take home immediately!</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $30-40 per couple<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your romantic candle experience!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Making candles together was so romantic and fun! We use them and think of our special date."</em></p>
      <p><strong>David & Sarah</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Perfect Valentine's Day date! We made matching candles with our favorite scents. So memorable!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Chris & Michelle</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Best date night ever! Creative, fun, and we left with beautiful candles we made together!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Ryan & Amber</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Date Night Pottery Painting</h3>
        <p>Romantic pottery painting experience for couples.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-classes/date-night-pottery-painting" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Pottery and Candle Combo Session</h3>
        <p>Experience both pottery and candle making in one creative session.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/pottery-and-candle-combo-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Adult Candle Making Night</h3>
        <p>Adult-focused candle making experience perfect for group events.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/adult-candle-making-night" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
